Package com.ibm.di.entry

Provides classes that implement the Security Directory Integrator Entry model.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttributeInterface Deprecated
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attribute
    The Attribute class is used in conjunction with the Entry object to store information about an attribute.
    AttributeValue
    The AttributeValue class is used in conjunction with the Attribute object to store information about an attribute value.
    CharacterDataImpl  
    DeltaEntry
    This class implements static methods to perform Delta operations on Entries and Attributes.
    DocImpl
    This class is just a place holder for all the methods that are not relevant to the IBM Tivoli Directory Integrator's DOM implementation and that are not implemented.
    Entry
    The Entry class is a container for attributes and their values.
    ModificationItem  
    NameTokenizer
    Tokenizer used for reading TDI attribute names.
    NodeImpl
    Basic implementation of the Node interface.
    Property
    This class represents the attribute in terms of XML concepts.
    PropertyMap
